indexes.index_definition: CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_client_entity_id ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (client_entity_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_client_id ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (client_id) WHERE (client_id IS NOT NULL)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_client_tax_id ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (client_tax_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_contract_id ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (contract_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_holding ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (holding_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_issue_date ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (issue_date)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_odoo_integration_id ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (odoo_integration_id)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_odoo_integration_unique ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (holding_id, odoo_integration_id) WHERE (odoo_integration_id IS NOT NULL)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_reconciliation_status ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (reconciliation_status)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_legacy_status ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (status)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX invoices_legacy_holding_invoice_number_unique ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (holding_id, invoice_number)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX invoices_legacy_pkey ON public.invoices_legacy USING btree (id)
